practitioner.about: Dr. Ayman Shouman is a Consultant Ophthalmologist at the Sheikh Zayed Road branch of Medcare Eye Centre. He completed his MBBCh from Cairo University and his MD from Cairo University, both in Cairo, Egypt. He holds a Fellowship from the Royal College of Physicians and Surgeons (FRCS), Glasgow. He is a member of the Examiner Board of the Royal College of Surgeons England, the American Academy of Ophthalmology and the European Society of Cataract and Refractive Surgeries. Dr. Shouman has worked in many countries including Egypt, the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia, the Sultanate of Oman and the United Arab Emirates. He commenced his meritorious career with a Residency at the Research Institute of Ophthalmology, Egypt and went on to do a Fellowship in Vitreoretinal surgery at the Frankfurt University in Germany. He then served as a Consultant Ophthalmic Surgeon at the New Jeddah Clinic Hospital in Saudi Arabia and the Eye Subspecialty Center in Egypt. He was appointed as a Senior Consultant Oph thalmic Surgeon at Alnahda Hospital in Oman. He continues to visit the Research Institute of Ophthalmology as a Professor of Ophthalmology. In Dubai, he practiced as a Consultant Ophthalmic Surgeon with the Saudi German Hospital, the Belhoul European Hospi tal, the Emirates Hospital Day Surgery and Medical Center and the Spanish Center. Dr. Shouman performs a wide range of ophthalmic procedures, including Argon laser, YAG laser, lens and retinal surgeries. He is an expert in vitreoretinal surgery (diabetic & detachment), retinal laser treatment, intraocular injections, retinopathy of prematurity, cataract and intraocular lens implantation, and Uveitis management. He has successfully performed retinal detachment procedure, Pars Plana Vitrectomy, proliferative diabetic retinopathy, macular hole, giant breaks, macular pucker, foreign body removal, intravitreal injections, Phacoemulsification, premium IOLs, combined cataract and glaucoma, Argon laser in diabetic retinopathy, Yag capsulotomy, Yag laser vitreolysis, glaucoma surgery, trabeculectomy, express valve implantation, selective Laser trabeculoplasty, cyclo cryotherapy, cyclo photocoagulation, ISTENT and PRESERFLOW. During his leisure hours, he likes to read, listen to music and dabble in some gardening. He keeps fit through swimming, playing Tennis and other sports. He speaks Arabic and English.

locations.about:
Medcare Eye Centre is a premier facility for comprehensive eye care in Dubai. We offer specialized treatment for refractive errors, congenital disorders, diseases, and eye injuries in both adults and children. Our state-of-the-art diagnostic and therapeutic technology, including laser treatments, enables our world-class team of ophthalmologists to provide high-precision, guideline-based care to patients of all ages, from neonates to senior citizens.

Expert Eye Doctors for Children & Adults

Our team comprises experts from internationally recognized universities, equipped with extensive clinical expertise and experience. They are skilled in diagnosing and treating a wide range of eye conditions in both children and adults. Medcare is proud to have a multi-lingual team of ophthalmologists, paediatric ophthalmologists, and optometrists dedicated to delivering the best possible eye care.

Comprehensive Eye Services

We conduct thorough assessments of eye health, including screening for common eye diseases and evaluating overall visual function. Utilizing advanced diagnostic tools and techniques, we diagnose and treat a wide range of eye diseases. Our vision correction solutions are tailored to meet individual needs, offering options such as eyeglasses, contact lenses, and refractive surgeries including LASIK, SMILE, PRESBYOND, and PRK.

Services Provided

Our services include cataract surgery, refractive surgery, glaucoma management, retinal disease management, and paediatric ophthalmology.

At Medcare, our philosophy is to provide unparalleled care for each patient, creating warm, patient-friendly environments to facilitate better and faster healing.

Discover our specialties at Sheikh Zayed Road - Medcare Eye Centre.
